## Scenarios

```isl
scenarios BehaviorName {
  scenario "description" {
    given {
      // Setup: bind variables
      var_name = expression
    }
    when {
      // Action: invoke behavior
      result = BehaviorName(param: value)
    }
    then {
      // Assertions
      result is success
      result.field == expected
    }
  }
}
```

